{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 1959, "height": 2682, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "3.宗祠匾额与楹联", "block_bbox": [726, 255, 1093, 304], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "大门：", "block_bbox": [272, 330, 381, 370], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜氏宗祠", "block_bbox": [271, 394, 447, 436], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "注：此匾额为2008年重修渑池坻坞杜氏宗祠而设。木质黑底，阴刻金字。", "block_bbox": [270, 462, 1574, 506], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "洪洞迁民四祖一叶卜居崤渑", "block_bbox": [269, 528, 770, 572], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "坻坞立家两门四派分播神州", "block_bbox": [268, 595, 770, 638], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "注：渑池杜氏十八世杜建成撰。木质黑底，阴刻蓝字。上联指渑池杜氏乃明洪武年间从山西洪洞迁出，当时弟兄四人破锅分迁，其一居渑，名讳失考，称“流芳”公云；下联指流芳公居于渑池之坻坞西村（今称“上西村”），二世忠、孝分为东西两门，东门又分三光、三乐、三元共三派，西门另迁惟杜金一派有传。其后，渑池杜氏分迁于宜阳、洛宁、漾鼻等地。\n", "block_bbox": [184, 663, 1617, 975], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "二门：", "block_bbox": [270, 996, 379, 1039], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "佑启后人", "block_bbox": [269, 1062, 446, 1105], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "注：此额于门框上方，为清乾隆年间创修宗祠时建，阳文砖刻。2008年漆绘为金字。杜氏祖先以无量功德庇荫后代。建造祠堂，尊祖敬宗，意在启迪后人发扬祖德。\n", "block_bbox": [183, 1132, 1616, 1304], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "不染似莲花，经世何妨出世；", "block_bbox": [269, 1328, 790, 1371], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "真空如水月，禅机即是文机。", "block_bbox": [270, 1393, 791, 1436], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "注：此联转自山东滨州市杜家卧佛台私垫楹联。2008年重修宗祠时制，木质黑底，阴刻蓝字。颇为形象地反映出山东杜氏家族的思想内核，映衬出滨州杜氏家族久盛不衰的历史因缘。上联中，“不染似莲花”是个人的道德修养是为人处世的基础。“何妨”是福祸相依的辩证法，反映出为社会政治服务的“经世”思想和超越世俗功利的“出世”思想境界；下联中，反映出身在仕途而心向山林，身受衣食役使而\n", "block_bbox": [183, 1458, 1617, 1836], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "精神保持淡泊清静，儒释道三教合一的丰富精神世界和文学价值观。此语当为中华杜氏处世箴言。\n", "block_bbox": [184, 1858, 1613, 1969], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 14}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "大殿外：", "block_bbox": [271, 1995, 423, 2036], "block_id": 14, "block_order": 15}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "甘棠重荫", "block_bbox": [271, 2060, 447, 2104], "block_id": 15, "block_order": 16}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "注：此匾额木质黑底，阴刻蓝字。", "block_bbox": [270, 2129, 875, 2172], "block_id": 16, "block_order": 17}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "周建国秦封爵唐拜相溯古三千年士族无双留衣冠", "block_bbox": [270, 2195, 1140, 2240], "block_id": 17, "block_order": 18}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "居京兆卜襄阳迁河南期后亿万世庶民有责兴中华", "block_bbox": [270, 2261, 1140, 2307], "block_id": 18, "block_order": 19}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "注：渑池杜氏十八世杜建成撰。上联记述了杜氏三千多年的历史。西周初，周成王时以桐叶封弟叔虞于唐（即后之晋国)，而将原封于唐地的尧帝后裔改封", "block_bbox": [186, 2328, 1615, 2438], "block_id": 19, "block_order": 20}, {"block_label": "aside_text", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [1734, 726, 1807, 1402], "block_id": 20, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "三六八", "block_bbox": [1741, 2026, 1790, 2139], "block_id": 21, "block_order": 21}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9454155564308167, "coordinate": [184.267822265625, 663.817138671875, 1617.799072265625, 975.351318359375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "labe